                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120513-75-off426 t18120513-75-cd427"></join>, a peck and a half of oats, value 2 s. and three pecks of chaff, value 18 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18120513-75-victim769" type="victimName">
                     Abraham 
                     Scrivener
